Your syntax is incorrect.  
Instead of _args[]_, use just _args_.

The bracket syntax is only used during declaration, and when accessing an element.  
_[Arrays (The Java&amp;trade; Tutorials &amp;gt; Learning the Java Language &amp;gt; Language Basics)](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/java/nutsandbolts/arrays.html)_.

Additionally, you&#39;re attempting to access _args_ elements which may not exist.  
If _args_ has no elements, then these will throw an _[ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException.html)_.

```java
